providerDescription: Hayhouse Projects is a professional sequencing operation run by Hackworth, a Genesis Sequencer for Aztec. My infrastructure is built for resilience, centered on a high-availability cluster with three geographically diversified nodes to ensure maximum uptime and performance. I am an operator with deep roots in the Ethereum ecosystem, having run infrastructure since the network's early days. My experience includes serving as a trusted public operator for SSV network (since the 2021 testnet) and managing a cluster of SDVT operators for the Lido protocol. I am committed to providing rock-solid, reliable infrastructure for the new frontier of Ethereum
